Name: Lord I cant even walk - lied
ChorusText:
Lord
i
can’t even walk
without you holding my hand
some mountains are too high
and the valleys too wide
but down on my knees
i’ve
learned how to stand
Lord
i
can’t even walk
without you holding my hand
I thought that no one
would surely be me
I thought that
i
could be
what
i
wanted to be
i
thought that
i
could be old
on life sinking sand
but
i
can’t even walk
without you holding my hand
I thought that
i
could
do a lot on my own
i
thought
i
could
make it all alone
i
thought of myself
as a mighty big man
but
i
cant even walk
without You holding my hand
